data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath brick ranch was recently updated with a new roof, new HVAC, new flooring, new light fixtures, new paint throughout, and an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances! This home has many energy efficient features to include solar panels that were installed in 2021, and a completely insulated and sealed attic. The prior owners electric bill averaged around $20/month! The spacious oversized 2 car garage allows plenty of space for 2 vehicles and a golf cart or a work space at the back of the garage. The shed in the backyard allows for even more storage! The mature and well maintained landscaping create instant curb appeal and the fenced in backyard allows for plenty of privacy while enjoying your pergola on your back patio. All this home is missing is YOU!
